<br>
Earned my epic about a year and a half ago.  I was pretty elated, and ol goner saw a lot of action.  I have pretty much retired him, but the staff has excellent stats and I equip it when I need the resist boost.<br>
<br>
As far as solo, I use my 61 air pet. I solo the cleric spiders in pod.  Stuns work great, pet has super regen, and I burn the mobs down.  Throw in mend companion with hastened mend3 and 64 pet heal and I only limited by my aggro.<br>
<br>
I have used ol goner in the same location, same mobs and it's been my experience that I have to spend more mana to keep him up and going.  It comes down to a matter of expedience and for me I have to choose the air pet as my preferred pet in almost all situations, be it raids, exp groups or solo.<br>
<br>
I have all the PoP pets and I use my air pet 95 percent of the time.<br>
